# API Query Budget

## Mandatory query counter

- Every HTTP route must track SQL queries per request (use `internal/metrics` or a shared middleware/helper).
- Expose count in logs and/or Prometheus for observability.

## High-query routes

- If a single request executes **> 10 queries**, document it in `docs/HIGH_QUERY_ROUTES.md`:
  - route, method, typical query count, reason, follow-up to reduce.

## Goal

Prevent N+1 patterns and memory pressure in production; flag routes for later optimization.
